                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200918-238-off1372 t18200918-238-cd1373"></join>, one watch, value 2 l., and one seal, value 2 s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18200918-238-victim2264" type="victimName">
                        Hezekiah 
                        Shepherd
                     <interp inst="t18200918-238-victim2264" type="surname" value="Shepherd"></interp>
